Lines.ff66a385-d3ff-3c12-0387-fa36ac476c11: The friends like us! We know... we see their thoughts!
Lines.26d3d424-1271-6f76-5cc5-0a1a47a94806: So many friends! So many thoughts! We see all... they make Us happy!
Lines.efa490aa-6041-230e-cb30-b3cab77520af: Us is happy! Us is fierce! Us is friendly! Us is here!
Lines.4d2d920c-e5db-5c61-b5d6-e8d4e7befa5c: So are we. So many friends! We are here for them! They make Us happy!
Lines.0a014c4c-1690-a8d8-1911-8ef488c4de5d: You love Us! And Us loves you!
Lines.f57983b0-5cf7-3e2a-8125-ca76cc66742a: We are a predator. Kitties are predators! They are like family to Us. We miss them... friends make Us happy!
Lines.4a09447b-7718-b2e7-3eb6-f9dbec8938af: Do not fret for Us! The kitties are good teachers. A mouse will feed us! A mouse will be our prey!
